*[[franchisor]]

===Etymology 2===
From French ''[[franchir]]''

====Verb====
{{conj|franchise|franchises|franchised|franchised|franchising}}
# ''(transitive)'' [[Confer]] certain powers on; grant a franchise to; [[authorize]].
# ''(transitive) (rare)'' Set free; [[invest]] with a franchise or [[privilege]]; [[enfranchise]].